├── Instinctive_Layer (Reptilian Brain)
│   ├── Fight-or-Flight Response
│   ├ Territorial Imperative
│   └── Reproductive Urge
├── Emotional_Layer (Limbic System)
│   ├── Confidence Assessment
│   ├── Social Hierarchy Processing
│   └── Threat Evaluation
└── Cognitive_Layer (Neocortex)
    ├── Strategic Planning
    ├── Pattern Recognition
    ├── Learning & Adaptation
